--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Paras Khadka, a veteran Nepali cricketer proved his worth once again by winning 
the Dhangadi Premier League. Under his captaincy, Nepal has won several international 
tournaments, including 2010 ICC World Cricket League Division Five, 2013 ICC World 
Cricket League Division Three and 2014 ICC World Cricket League Division Three. 
An idol of many aspiring cricketer, Paras has left no stone unturned when it comes 
to make our country proud.
